casebody.data:
Willie ROGERS, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
The STATE of Florida, Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D17-1972 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. SEPTEMBER 20, 2017 LAGOA, EMAS and SCALES, JJ., concur.

Following review of the petition for writ of mandamus and the response thereto, it is ordered that said petition is hereby denied without prejudice.
